<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Digital Grievance System</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1d2671, #c33764);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .container {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 900px;
      box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 35px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.8;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Digital Grievance System</h1>
      <p>A Secure & Anonymous Platform for Students</p>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>üîí Anonymous Complaints</h3>
        <p>
          Students can submit grievances without revealing their identity to
          departments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>üè¢ Department Tagging</h3>
        <p>
          Complaints are automatically routed to the relevant department for
          faster resolution.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>‚è± Time-Bound Resolution</h3>
        <p>
          Each complaint has a fixed deadline, ensuring accountability.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>üìà Auto Escalation</h3>
        <p>
          If not resolved on time, complaints are escalated to higher authorities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      ¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Digital Grievance System | College Project
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
